msgid "# Using Volcano Kthena"
msgstr "# 使用 Volcano Kthena"

msgid ""
"This guide shows how to run **prefill–decode (PD) disaggregation** on Huawei"
" Ascend NPUs using **vLLM-Ascend**, with "
"[**Kthena**](https://kthena.volcano.sh/) handling orchestration on "
"Kubernetes. About vLLM support with Kthena, please refer to [Deploy vLLM "
"with "
"Kthena](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/deployment/integrations/kthena/)."
msgstr ""
"本指南介绍如何使用 **vLLM-Ascend** 在华为昇腾 NPU 上运行 **预填充-解码（PD）分离**，并由 "
"[**Kthena**](https://kthena.volcano.sh/) 在 Kubernetes 上进行编排。关于 vLLM 对 Kthena"
" 的支持，请参考 [使用 Kthena 部署 "
"vLLM](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/deployment/integrations/kthena/)。"

msgid "## 2. Deploy on Kubernetes with Kthena"
msgstr "## 2. 使用 Kthena 在 Kubernetes 上部署"

msgid ""
"[Kthena](https://kthena.volcano.sh/) is a Kubernetes-native LLM inference "
"platform that transforms how organizations deploy and manage Large Language "
"Models in production. Built with declarative model lifecycle management and "
"intelligent request routing, it provides high-performance and enterprise-"
"grade scalability for LLM inference workloads. In this example, we use three"
" key Custom Resource Definitions (CRDs):"
msgstr ""
"[Kthena](https://kthena.volcano.sh/) 是一个 Kubernetes 原生的 LLM "
"推理平台，它改变了组织在生产环境中部署和管理大型语言模型的方式。它采用声明式模型生命周期管理和智能请求路由构建，为 LLM "
"推理工作负载提供高性能和企业级可扩展性。在此示例中，我们使用三个关键的自定义资源定义（CRD）："

msgid ""
"- `ModelServing` — defines the workloads (prefill and decode roles).\n"
"- `ModelServer` — manages PD groupings and internal routing.\n"
"- `ModelRoute` — exposes a stable model endpoint."
msgstr ""
"- `ModelServing` — 定义工作负载（预填充和解码角色）。\n"
"- `ModelServer` — 管理 PD 分组和内部路由。\n"
"- `ModelRoute` — 暴露稳定的模型端点。"

msgid ""
"This section uses the `deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite` example, but you can "
"swap in any model supported by vLLM-Ascend."
msgstr "本节以 `deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite` 为例，但您可以替换为 vLLM-Ascend 支持的任何模型。"

msgid "### 2.1 Prerequisites"
msgstr "### 2.1 前提条件"

msgid "- Kubernetes cluster with Ascend NPU nodes:"
msgstr "- 包含昇腾 NPU 节点的 Kubernetes 集群："

msgid ""
"The resources corresponding to different NPU Drivers may vary slightly. For "
"example:"
msgstr "不同 NPU 驱动对应的资源可能略有不同。例如："

msgid ""
"- If using [MindCluster](https://gitee.com/ascend/mind-"
"cluster#https://gitee.com/link?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgitcode.com%2FAscend%2Fmind-"
"cluster), please use `huawei.com/Ascend310P` or `huawei.com/Ascend910`."
msgstr ""
"- 如果使用 [MindCluster](https://gitee.com/ascend/mind-"
"cluster#https://gitee.com/link?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgitcode.com%2FAscend%2Fmind-"
"cluster)，请使用 `huawei.com/Ascend310P` 或 `huawei.com/Ascend910`。"

msgid ""
"- If running on CCE (Cloud Container Engine) of Huawei Cloud and the [CCE AI"
" Suite Plugin (Ascend NPU)](https://support.huaweicloud.com/intl/en-"
"us/usermanual-cce/cce_10_0239.html) is installed, please use "
"`huawei.com/ascend-310` or `huawei.com/ascend-1980`."
msgstr ""
"- 如果在华为云 CCE（云容器引擎）上运行，并且已安装 [CCE AI 套件插件（昇腾 "
"NPU）](https://support.huaweicloud.com/intl/en-us/usermanual-"
"cce/cce_10_0239.html)，请使用 `huawei.com/ascend-310` 或 "
"`huawei.com/ascend-1980`。"

msgid ""
"- Kthena installed. Please follow the [Kthena installation "
"guide](https://kthena.volcano.sh/docs/getting-started/installation)."
msgstr ""
"- 已安装 Kthena。请遵循 [Kthena 安装指南](https://kthena.volcano.sh/docs/getting-"
"started/installation)。"

msgid ""
"### 2.2 Deploy Prefill-Decode Disaggregated DeepSeek-V2-Lite on Kubernetes"
msgstr "### 2.2 在 Kubernetes 上部署预填充-解码分离的 DeepSeek-V2-Lite"

msgid ""
"A concrete example is provided in Kthena as <https://github.com/volcano-"
"sh/kthena/blob/main/examples/model-serving/prefill-decode-"
"disaggregation.yaml>"
msgstr ""
"Kthena 中提供了一个具体示例，位于 <https://github.com/volcano-"
"sh/kthena/blob/main/examples/model-serving/prefill-decode-"
"disaggregation.yaml>"

msgid "Deploy it with the command below:"
msgstr "使用以下命令部署："

msgid "You should see Pods such as:"
msgstr "您应该会看到如下 Pod："

msgid ""
"- `deepseek-v2-lite-0-prefill-0-0`\n"
"- `deepseek-v2-lite-0-decode-0-0`"
msgstr ""
"- `deepseek-v2-lite-0-prefill-0-0`\n"
"- `deepseek-v2-lite-0-decode-0-0`"

msgid ""
"To enable the LLM access, we still need to configure the routing layer with "
"`ModelServer` and `ModelRoute`."
msgstr "要启用 LLM 访问，我们还需要使用 `ModelServer` 和 `ModelRoute` 配置路由层。"

msgid "### 2.3 ModelServer: PD Group Management"
msgstr "### 2.3 ModelServer：PD 组管理"

msgid "The `ModelServer` resource:"
msgstr "`ModelServer` 资源："

msgid ""
"- Selects the `ModelServing` workloads via labels.\n"
"- Groups prefill and decode Pods into PD pairs.\n"
"- Configures KV connector details and timeouts.\n"
"- Exposes an internal gRPC/HTTP interface."
msgstr ""
"- 通过标签选择 `ModelServing` 工作负载。\n"
"- 将预填充和解码 Pod 分组为 PD 对。\n"
"- 配置 KV 连接器详细信息和超时。\n"
"- 暴露内部 gRPC/HTTP 接口。"

msgid "Create ModelServer with the command below:"
msgstr "使用以下命令创建 ModelServer："

msgid "### 2.4 ModelRoute: User-Facing Endpoint"
msgstr "### 2.4 ModelRoute：面向用户的端点"

msgid ""
"The `ModelRoute` resource maps a model name (e.g., `\"deepseek-"
"ai/DeepSeekV2\"`) to the `ModelServer`."
msgstr "`ModelRoute` 资源将模型名称（例如 `\"deepseek-ai/DeepSeekV2\"`）映射到 `ModelServer`。"

msgid "Example manifest:"
msgstr "示例清单："

msgid "## 3. Verification"
msgstr "## 3. 验证"

msgid "### 3.1 Check Workloads"
msgstr "### 3.1 检查工作负载"

msgid "Confirm that prefill and decode Pods are up:"
msgstr "确认预填充和解码 Pod 已启动："

msgid "You should see both roles in `Running` and `Ready` state."
msgstr "您应该看到两个角色都处于 `Running` 和 `Ready` 状态。"

msgid "### 3.2 Test the Chat Endpoint"
msgstr "### 3.2 测试聊天端点"

msgid ""
"Once routing is configured, you can send a test request to the Kthena-"
"router:"
msgstr "路由配置完成后，您可以向 Kthena-router 发送测试请求："

msgid "A successful JSON response confirms that:"
msgstr "成功的 JSON 响应确认了："

msgid ""
"- The prefill and decode services are both running on Ascend NPUs.\n"
"- KV transfer between them is working.\n"
"- The Kthena routing layer is correctly fronting the vLLM-Ascend plugin."
msgstr ""
"- 预填充和解码服务均在昇腾 NPU 上运行。\n"
"- 它们之间的 KV 传输正常工作。\n"
"- Kthena 路由层正确地前置了 vLLM-Ascend 插件。"

msgid "## 4. Cleanup"
msgstr "## 4. 清理"

msgid "To remove the deployment:"
msgstr "要移除部署："

msgid "## 5. Summary"
msgstr "## 5. 总结"

msgid ""
"For more advanced features, please refer to the [Kthena "
"website](https://kthena.volcano.sh/)."
msgstr "更多高级功能，请参考 [Kthena 网站](https://kthena.volcano.sh/)。"

msgid "or"
msgstr "或"

msgid "## 1. What is Prefill–Decode Disaggregation?"
msgstr ""

msgid "Large language model inference naturally splits into two phases:"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"- **Prefill**\n"
"    - Processes input tokens and builds the key–value (KV) cache.\n"
"    - Batch-friendly, high-throughput, well-suited to parallel NPU execution.\n"
"- **Decode**\n"
"    - Consumes the KV cache to generate output tokens.\n"
"    - Latency-sensitive, memory-intensive, more sequential."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"From the client's perspective, this still looks like a single Chat / "
"Completions endpoint."
msgstr ""
